- **Admin Audit Overview**

**Overview**

This dashboard displays key statistics and visualizations based on admin audit event logs from the CyberArk EPM integration. It includes the top source IPs, administrators, and activities; a breakdown of events by assigned role and feature; along with a time-based event trend line chart and essential details about admin audit event data.

[**Integration Page**](/app/integrations/detail/cyberark_epm/overview)
